value.string: Purpose: Opens SAP environment either as SSO or with Log-In credentials in credential vault
Notes: Input variables- set sSapSSOEnvironments to true to use single sign on and false to use the credential vault
Notes: Input variables- set sSapServerEnvironment for SAP environment bot should access
Notes: For sign in to SAP without SSO:
---Credential Variables Used: EMEA Locker, SAP Lauchpad UAT, Username
---Credential Variables Used: EMEA Locker, SAP Lauchpad UAT, Password
Continue with this logon and end any other logons in the system.
